###

### ==========================================
### REGENERATE ANOTHER DAY
### ==========================================

PUT http://localhost:5000/api/trips/TRIP_ID/regenerate-day
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "day": 5,
  "instruction": "Focus on food and cultural experiences"
}

###

### ==========================================
### DELETE TRIP
### Replace TRIP_ID
### ==========================================

DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/trips/TRIP_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

